<p>In every piece, the pair express their deep love and appreciation for their culture and identity as Aboriginal women. </p>

<p>The collection was launched online and in stores on September 24 and less than 24 hours later many of the popular products have already sold out online. </p>

<p>'Fantastic! I signed up before placing my order this morning. Can't wait for my order to arrive. Congratulations on the huge success of your range; I knew they'd sell out quick,' one woman wrote on the official Miimi and Jiinda Facebook page.</p>

<p>Adairs customers were thrilled by the collaboration and have been busy purchasing all manner of cushions, towels and throws</p>

